        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Allows the caller to pass in a point which is processed and the <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1TouchEvent" kindref="compound">TouchEvent</ref> and/or <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1HoverEvent" kindref="compound">HoverEvent</ref> is appropriately filled with the new, and previously stored <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1Point" kindref="compound">Point</ref> information.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>If the thresholds set have not been passed, then false is returned and the <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1TouchEvent" kindref="compound">TouchEvent</ref> and/or <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1HoverEvent" kindref="compound">HoverEvent</ref> should not be sent to <ref refid="namespaceDali" kindref="compound">Dali</ref> <ref refid="classDali_1_1Integration_1_1Core" kindref="compound">Core</ref>.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">point</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The new <ref refid="structDali_1_1Integration_1_1Point" kindref="compound">Point</ref>. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">time</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The time the event occurred. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">touchEvent</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>This is populated with the correct Point(s) and time information. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">hoverEvent</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>This is populated with the correct Point(s) and time information. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">isMultiTouchEvent</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The Flag whether multitouch is being.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>true if the point is beyond the different thresholds set thus, should be sent to core, false otherwise. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
